{"type":null,"faqId":40430,"title":"如何设置计算机IP地址和MAC地址绑定？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.s1{font-family:Times New Roman;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>将计算机的</span><span class=\"s1\">IP</span><span>地址与</span><span class=\"s1\">MAC</span><span>地址绑定，可以有效防止</span><span class=\"s1\">ARP</span><span>攻击。绑定以后，计算机</span><span class=\"s1\">IP</span><span>地址与</span><span class=\"s1\">MAC</span><span>地址是一一对应的关系，其他人无法通过</span><span class=\"s1\">ARP</span><span>攻击来盗用计算机</span><span class=\"s1\">IP</span><span>地址，您就可以正常使用网络了。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>登录路由器Web配置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>进入“</span><span class=\"s3\">更多功能 &gt; 网络设置 &gt;局域网</span><span>”页面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s3\">静态IP地址绑定列表</span><span>”中，单击右侧的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137252\" style=\"width:0.24930556in;height:0.21041666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> 图标，添加一条绑定规则。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137253\" style=\"width:5.513889in;height:1.6555556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><a name=\"OLE_LINK22\"><span>在弹出的“</span><span class=\"s3\">添加静态IP地址绑定</span><span>”对话框中，填写要绑定的设备“</span><span class=\"s3\">MAC地址</span><span>”，指定其静态“</span><span class=\"s3\">IP地址</span><span>”，并自定义设备“</span><span class=\"s3\">主机</span><span>”名称，</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">保存</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137254\" style=\"width:3.9375in;height:2.8416667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>返回“</span><span class=\"s3\">静态IP地址绑定列表</span><span>”，打开刚刚添加的绑定规则的“</span><span class=\"s3\">启用</span><span>”开关即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137255\" style=\"width:5.508333in;height:1.6597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5777","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768487000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}